+# AutoEgoAI Golden Loop Runbook
+
+## Goal
+Run a 5-cycle improvement chain where each cycle produces verifiable deliverables and updates the ledger.
+
+## Cycle structure (PDCA)
+1) Plan: objective + metric
+2) Do: deliverable(s)
+3) Check: verification/eval step
+4) Act: update prompt/ledger; lock improvement
+
+## When blocked
+Use the fallback ladder in prompts/autoegoai_system_prompt.md
